  "keyFeatures": [
    "Type-safe chess position representation with bitboards",
    "FEN, PGN, and SAN notation parsing and writing",
    "Legal move generation for chess and variants",
    "Support for 8 chess variants including Chess960",
    "Streaming PGN parser with game tree support",
    "Attack calculation using Hyperbola Quintessence",
    "Position validation and game outcome detection",
    "Board transformations (mirroring, rotation)"
